title: OPPO F1s Rose Gold Limited Edition launched in India for Rs 18,990
text:
OPPO F1s Rose Gold Limited Edition launched in India for Rs 18,990 OPPO F1s Rose Gold Limited Edition launched in India for Rs 18,990 By   OPPO F1s is a selfie-centric smartphone with a 16-megapixel front-facing camera‚Äù 
OPPO has announced the launch of the F1s Rose Gold Limited Edition smartphone in India. The new colour variant of the phone is priced at Rs 18,990, and will be available exclusively on Flipkart starting February 10th. It is already available to pre-order on the e-tailer. 
Apart from the new gold rose hue, the new OPPO F1s ( review ) variant offers the same internals as the regular model. It is a selfie-focussed offering with a 16-megapixel front-facing shooter. It offers a 5.5-inch HD display, an octa-core MediaTek MT6750 SoC, 4GB of RAM, 64GB of storage, a 13MP rear camera, 4G LTE, VoLTE, Android Lollipop and a 3,075mAh battery. Facebook Comments
